Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.68,0:36:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,even more examples.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.69,0:36:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can see how we do this in
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.71,0:36:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Interface Builder.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.99,0:36:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see an example where we
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.40,0:36:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,wrap text around images.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.56,0:36:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can find a case where we
