Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.38,0:36:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,necessary for larger fonts, and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.30,0:36:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,more.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.28,0:36:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of it as a recipe book for
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.67,0:36:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,things you might encounter in
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.82,0:36:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,your own apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.97,0:36:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So we highly encourage you to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.38,0:36:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,check it out after the session.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.57,0:36:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,To summarize what we covered
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.51,0:36:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,today, it's easy to support
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.56,0:36:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dynamic Type with new API in iOS
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.84,0:36:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,11.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.14,0:37:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have an app that doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.53,0:37:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,support Dynamic Type, now is a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.38,0:37:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,great time to do so, and you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.20,0:37:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,should because supporting
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.46,0:37:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dynamic Type is good for your
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.05,0:37:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,users.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.60,0:37:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good for the users who
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.72,0:37:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,prefer smaller text because it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.62,0:37:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,allows them to see more on
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.73,0:37:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.09,0:37:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good for the users who
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.00,0:37:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,prefer larger text because it's
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.58,0:37:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,more comfortable to read, and
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.89,0:37:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it's especially beneficial for
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.83,0:37:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,users who need larger text in
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.85,0:37:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,order to be able to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.55,0:37:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When more apps are usable by
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.23,0:37:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,people with a disability, such
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.77,0:37:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,as low vision, it really helps
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.26,0:37:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to level the playing field for
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.01,0:37:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,those users.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.46,0:37:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so by supporting Dynamic
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.89,0:37:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Type in your app, you're
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.31,0:37:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,actually making the world a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.26,0:37:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.70,0:37:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So we really hope you take what
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.36,0:37:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you saw today in today's session
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.48,0:37:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and go back and make apps that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.38,0:37:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,work well with Dynamic Type and
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.04,0:37:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,include more users so that more
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.61,0:37:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,users can benefit from the great
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.61,0:37:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,work you've done.
